snippet: The U.S. judge overseeing a criminal drug prosecution against FedEx Corp said one of the core issues will be what FedEx executives knew about illegal online pharmacies whose packages it shipped....

headline.print_headline: What FedEx Knew of Online Pharmacies Is Key Issue in Drug Case: Judge
headline.main: What FedEx Knew of Online Pharmacies Is Key Issue in Drug Case: Judge

lead_paragraph: The U.S. judge overseeing a criminal drug prosecution against FedEx Corp said one of the core issues will be what FedEx executives knew about illegal online pharmacies whose packages it shipped.
